---
Compare a URL against known-good patterns

Usage: tirith diff [OPTIONS] <URL>

Arguments:
  <URL>  URL to analyze

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format (default: human) [possible values: human, json]
  -h, --help             Print help

Examples:
  tirith diff https://install.example-cli.dev
  tirith diff --format json https://install.example-cli.dev
